name: Artemis
description:
Artemis is my favorite character in Greek mythology, I painted this art for a  long time, but I could not finish, I was waiting for special inspiration,
And then the days came when I experienced very strong emotions associated with the departure of a loved one, I was left alone and looked for light in my art, as always, this art is inspired by the image of my wife, there is no thought of her, leave me, even after she left me
